flowchart LR
    A[Checkout Code] --> B[npm ci]
    B --> C[Cache Playwright<br/>Browser Binary]
    C --> D[npx diagramkit warmup]
    D --> E["npx diagramkit render .<br/>--json --format svg"]
    E --> F{Failures?}
    F -->|No| G[Upload Artifacts<br/>or Commit Outputs]
    F -->|Yes| H[Fail Build<br/>Report Errors]
